data.description: GORGEOUS LOCATION HIGH UP ON THE HILL - VIEWS!! FABULOUS BACK YARD WITH COVERED PATIO, CUSTOM CONCRETE, GORGEOUS FOUNTAIN SPA IS HALF SUNK IN GROUND FOR EASY ACCESS.  KITCHEN WAS REMODELED ABOUT 2 YEARS AGO AND IS FABULOUS WITH NEW CABINETS, ISLAND STAINLESS APPLIANCES AND SO MUCH MORE CUSTOM TILE FLOORING THROUGHOUT MOST OF HOUSE.  AMAZING FIREPLACE IN GREAT ROOM, OPEN FLOOR PLAN.  DEN WITH BUILT INS JUST OFF GREAT ROOM.  LARGE PRIMARY SUITE WITH DOOR LEADING TO BACK YARD AND SPA  HIGH CEILINGS FOR SPACIOUS FEEL CONNECTED SPA SUITE WITH TUB AND SHOWER AND CUSTOM CLOSET THAT MAXIMIZES STORAGE.  BEDROOM 2 HAS CEILING FAN.  THERE IS AN AMAZING OFFICE IN THE GARAGE AREA WITH BUILT INS THERE TOO!  LAUNDRY IS IN GARAGE AND INCLUDES NEWER WASHER AND DRYER.    ROLLADEN SHUTTERS ON THE OUTSIE AND SHUTTERS INSIDE AND UPGRADES GALORE!  GOLF CART PARKING AND ALL THE AMENITIES SUN CITY HAS TO OFFER.
